Program: The Reith Lectures
Title: War And The Individual
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00gw9ws
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 29 Apr 1998
This year's Reith lecturer is British military historian and journalist John Keegan. In his fourth Reith lecture, recorded at the Bute Hall, University of Glasgow, John Keegan considers the impact of battle on those who fight them and how it's altered the nature of war throughout history. He also examines how modern warfare has changed the role and experiences of the soldier. Show less